text: chaur anak( mou ham meat) pol tha brasenbae a l laoh mean chetnea( min aoy khnhom sautr kompir kuor an) khnhom ka minban sautr vea aoy puok anak sdab der haey trong ka minban thveu aoy puok anakdoeng ampi vea der . pit brakd nasa khnhom ban rsanow knongchamnaom puok anak asa muoy rykal der moun vea( moun pel ke banhchouh vea hi) . tae puok anak min pichearna te ryy
